<font face="arial" size=4>

Welcome to the world of The Associates!  We are a 
leading provider of financial services to 
consumers and businesses throughout the United 
States and internationally.  We are the nation's 
second largest independent finance company, and we 
are dedicated to serving the financial needs of 
our customers.<p>

<a href="corp/hot/"><img border=0 align=right src="images/whatshot.gif"></a>We help consumers meet their financial needs through a variety of products, including home equity-secured loans, personal loans, retail sales financing and credit card financing.<p>

Our commercial services include transportation, industrial and communications equipment financing and leasing, as well as a variety of specialized programs for businesses of all sizes.<p>

<a href="corp/overview/">The Associates</a> has more than 1,950 consumer branches and commercial finance offices to meet your needs.  And, beyond our domestic borders, we offer an array of services through offices in <a href="corp/international/index.html#japan">Japan</a>, <a href="corp/international/index.html#canada">Canada</a>, <a href="corp/international/index.html#mexico">Mexico</a>, <a href="corp/international/index.html#puertorico">Puerto Rico</a> and the <a href="corp/international/index.html#uk">United Kingdom</a>. Click here to view our <a href=http://www.reportgallery.com/associates/>1996 Annual Report</a>.<p>

